<section class="home-section home-section--alt">
  <div class="home-section__inner">
    <h2 class="home-section__title">Lesson Phases</h2>
    <p class="home-section__subtitle">150 structured lessons across 7 phases, from counting to two-digit arithmetic.</p>
    <div class="phase-cards">
      <a href="/phases/phase-1/" class="phase-card">
        <span class="phase-card__badge">Phase 1</span>
        <h3 class="phase-card__title">Foundation</h3>
        <p class="phase-card__desc">Lessons 1&ndash;20. Numbers 0&ndash;10, counting, one-to-one correspondence, and comparing.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/phases/phase-2/" class="phase-card">
        <span class="phase-card__badge">Phase 2</span>
        <h3 class="phase-card__title">Counting &amp; Comparing</h3>
        <p class="phase-card__desc">Lessons 21&ndash;40. Numbers to 20, number patterns, and introduction to the plus symbol.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/phases/phase-3/" class="phase-card">
        <span class="phase-card__badge">Phase 3</span>
        <h3 class="phase-card__title">Addition</h3>
        <p class="phase-card__desc">Lessons 41&ndash;65. All addition facts to 10, doubles, number bonds, and the commutative property.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/phases/phase-4/" class="phase-card">
        <span class="phase-card__badge">Phase 4</span>
        <h3 class="phase-card__title">Subtraction</h3>
        <p class="phase-card__desc">Lessons 66&ndash;85. Subtraction facts to 10, fact families, and the relationship to addition.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/phases/phase-5/" class="phase-card">
        <span class="phase-card__badge">Phase 5</span>
        <h3 class="phase-card__title">Place Value</h3>
        <p class="phase-card__desc">Lessons 86&ndash;105. Tens and ones, counting to 100, and addition/subtraction within 20.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/phases/phase-6/" class="phase-card">
        <span class="phase-card__badge">Phase 6</span>
        <h3 class="phase-card__title">Fluency</h3>
        <p class="phase-card__desc">Lessons 106&ndash;125. Mental math strategies, make-10, and two-digit plus one-digit.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/phases/phase-7/" class="phase-card">
        <span class="phase-card__badge">Phase 7</span>
        <h3 class="phase-card__title">Mastery</h3>
        <p class="phase-card__desc">Lessons 126&ndash;150. Two-digit addition and subtraction with regrouping, and word problems.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

